loop-wrapper (2.3.1-1) precise; urgency=low

  * Enable alternative timesteps for looping (year, month, hour, ...) with the
    --every flag
  * Allow more dateformats for the START and STOP dates (e.g. YYYYMM or
    YYYYMMDDHH)
  * Rework the error handling and --die-on-error flag
  * Unit Testing, GitHub, GPLv2,...

 -- Thomas Lavergne <thomas.lavergne@met.no>  Tue, 26 May 2015 22:47:08 +0200
